_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.9999999617127749, \"rank\": 3.828728684559365e-08, \"text\": \"XY\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC said the rules of eligibility were based on those of the Tokyo Games in 2021 and cannot be changed during a competition.\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2460, \"end\": 2463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.761493896225758e-23, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The current aggression against these two athletes is based entirely on this arbitrary decision, which was taken without any proper procedure - especially considering that these athletes had been competing in top-level competition for many years,\\\" the IOC said.\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2838, \"end\": 2841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.761493896225758e-23, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The IOC is saddened by the abuse that the two athletes are currently receiving,\\\" it added.\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2940, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2854, \"end\": 2857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.761493896225758e-23, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every person has the right to practice sport without discrimination.\\\"\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 3011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement, the IBA condemned \\\"inconsistencies in eligibility\\\" at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3033, \"end\": 3036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9438182150883073, \"rank\": 0.059522249479986265, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Both Imane Khelif and Lin Yu-ting post testing, did not meet the required eligibility criteria to compete within the female category of our respective events,\\\" the body added.\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3107, \"end\": 3119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 3124, \"end\": 3135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The urgent nature of the decision (to disqualify the boxers) was justified, as the safety of our boxers is our top priority.\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3448, \"entities\